      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-D33DABAA-907D-4FDC-AB41-69EEEE959A2F" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-30EA3688-D94D-4B18-851D-0E9350641696" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2F0CD31E-8DB5-435A-B989-31846CCE3EE1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP to Differentiate Between ZDFP &amp; Milestone with Progress Payment ZDPP </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9A875D1A-34AC-4E73-9BE4-85209E85A893" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Contract to Dictate how many Progress payments to occur prior to true up </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DF594FC4-0761-4CDB-A270-AE0A6B913218" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Progress Payment ? 1:n This Process can repeat for each progress payment until each milestone is met </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F7C40E9A-5EE3-4B53-A98E-99623F9D8C92" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Similar to Cost contract order must be DMR SO but with ZD02 type and item category ZD04. 
2. Contract to remain active until final milestone billing </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-441053F6-067C-4EE6-989B-6F5C5AC9FD59" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Incase of Milestone with PP enabled, a milestone contract is used according to contract details </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E9550321-CEFF-45BB-9B7F-6B58A06A2B54" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. For Intel Federal Validate contract type ZDIF 
2. For milestone contract validate line item category ZD06 and billing block removal (after payment is approved in dassian) 
3. Similar to Milestone Contract order with PP must be with sales order item category ZD06. 
4. Contract viewed as complete upon billing of milestone trueup </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4AC09158-7A25-4D65-AC79-2B31D23C8B24" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>In case of Milestone Billing, for IFL Invoices Created in Reference to Contract no Sales Order Required </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-78CDFCC8-C287-4C0F-A38E-F929456A0646" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If Delivery relevant (for milestone Contract) Free of charge Sales Order Created </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-38B12931-7B49-41F7-BC1D-FAC150ADE216" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-67FF6676-FB2D-48CF-B10F-EEE4C0A3775C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. FSCM stands for Financial Supply Chain Management</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B9D05B0E-98B2-4EEB-9BB6-E9BFDC3CBD31" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0911988E-BFC4-487B-ADF3-71349FCF0E40" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#99CC00"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#99cc00" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#99cc00" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Processes are happening outside of Capture Order and are covered in subsequent L3s</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-3286e0af-2b16-4fb8-a922-b1b7348c595f" id="sid-CAFC35B9-3635-4281-9FD2-4C34ED0F2C0C">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-01B4C3B1-F992-4264-90F7-5B9C9BFEA474" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="18.0" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="18.0" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform Process Steward: Michel Al, Shawi &lt;michel.al.shawi@intel.com&gt;, and BPM Champion: Rebeca, Meza Redondo &lt;rebeca.meza.redondo@intel.com&gt; of any changes that occur within the flow from now onwards so that changes can be accurately reflected within BIC</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
